    <item>
      <title>新兴市场上涨，交易员关注中国和关键就业报告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/emerging-stocks-stall-as-traders-await-china-s-next-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者等待中国进一步刺激措施的潜在迹象和周五的美国就业报告，新兴市场股市连续第四个交易日上涨，货币几乎抹去了每周的跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/emerging-stocks-stall-as-traders-await-china-s-next-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 11:32:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大帝国商业银行 (CIBC) 营收和盈利超预期，股价创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/cibc-beats-as-credit-losses-decline-despite-economic-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大帝国商业银行 (Canadian Imperial Bank of Commerce) 的信用质量又一个季度好于预期，其美国业务显示出克服商业房地产问题迹象，因此业绩超出预期。该行股价上涨，创下 94.20 加元的历史新高，随后略有回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/cibc-beats-as-credit-losses-decline-despite-economic-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 10:42:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 计划推迟并减缓产量恢复速度，油价保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OPEC+宣布计划将增加供应量推迟三个月，但仍将从4月份开始向预计供应过剩的市场增产，油价在震荡交易中小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 23:34:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市陷入困境，就业市场预示美联储降息或暂停：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市在历史高点附近难以获得太大的吸引力，交易员们正在为关键的就业数据做准备，这些数据将有助于确定美联储 12 月份是降息还是维持利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 22:39:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
